readability_reflection: Interpolation is much more readable as there aren't many + signs. It can be confusing, especially when wanting to use a symbol in the concentration.
preference_rationale: I would choose string interpolation as it's much more readable and editable for future use.
learning_curve: Understanding basic syntax is important when looking at this, however, I believe anyone has the ability to do this. I'm sure I messed up along the way as there were times where there were too many quotation marks and symbols, but I believe my experience in CS has helped me with these problems.
